SPFv7 is free software (see file LICENSE) 

Please cite SPFv7 if you base any scientific 
publication on this software. Citation should read:
G. Alvarez, C. Sen, Q. Luo, Y. Yildirim (2011), SpinPhononFermion (version 7.1) 
[computer software], Oak Ridge National Laboratory.

---------------------------------------------------
The new code is in directory
v7/

and some models have already been ported
to the new clean conventions.

----------------------------------------------------
Dependencies and how to download:
cd someDirectory
git clone https://github.com/g1257/PsimagLite
git clone https://github.com/g1257/spf

----------------------------------------------------
cd spf/v7/
perl driver.pl
(answer questions) 
make
./spf input.inp

----------------------------------------------------
To update the code:
cd someDirectory
cd PsimagLite
git pull
cd ../spf/v7
git pull
----------------------------------------------------

